latestPosts.caption:
🌸 save the date, shift the way you create

beyond the algorithm — a live 2-day workshop by @storieswithneha & @bougainvillea.and.barni

📅 July 19th & 20th| 3:30-5:00pm | Google Meet | ₹1499 early bird | ₹1999 regular

It’s not that your content isn’t good.
It’s that you’re working in a world that forgets fast.
This workshop is our response to that fatigue —
a space to slow down, sharpen your craft, and finally… stand out.

🪷 What we’ll cover (Day 1)
– noticing like a creator (not a consumer)
– capturing without overthinking
– grid memory, visual identity, emotional editing
– content that converts: reels, carousels, captions
– monetization models, brand pitching, portfolio clarity

🧠 What you’ll do (Day 2)
– live edit review
– feedback from both of us — emotional + strategic
– real-time clarity on where you’re stuck and what can shift

🎁 What’s included:
– full PDF of the workshop
– algorithm checklist for 2025
– portfolio + invoice template
– repost chance for 5 standout entries

✏️ Want more after?
We’re building a 1-month follow-up space for you.
(Think: soft accountability + structured creative practice.)

This isn’t just about growing.
It’s about building something that fits you.
DM “ready” to register.
(or save this if it felt like it was meant for later.)
.
.
.
.
.
.

#desicore #desiaesthetics #desiaesthetics editing tips, content creation workshop, finding your niche, color grading, visual story telling, editing process
